 * - mode='v4_full' → 启用接管 (dynamic enabled + mvu disabled)
 * - mode='mvu_fallback' → 还原 (dynamic disabled + mvu enabled)
 * - mode='v4_degraded' → 同 mvu_fallback (自动降级触发)
